    "Longhurst never married; her estate was directed by her colleague, <a href=\"/molesworthh\">Hender Delves Molesworth</a>, who succeeded her in 1945.": [],
    "Her unpublished, which she hoped would be published, were edited in 1963, but never published.": [],
    "They remain at the Victoria and Albert Museum and at the University of London, Warburg Institute.": [],
